00:57:29,554 --> 00:57:32,284
Faster!
- ''Go...go...go...Govinda.''

1032
00:57:34,493 --> 00:57:35,790
That was a narrow escape.

1033
00:57:36,495 --> 00:57:38,554
Now, take me to Brahmanwadi.

1034
00:57:39,898 --> 00:57:45,359
Go straight then take a left,
then right and another left.

1035
00:57:45,837 --> 00:57:46,997
And you'll be home, go on.

1036
00:57:47,773 --> 00:57:50,264
You brought me this far,
so drop me home as well.

1037
00:57:50,308 --> 00:57:51,673
My job's to show the way..

1038
00:57:51,743 --> 00:57:53,404
..it's your job to
get to the destination.

1039
00:57:55,914 --> 00:57:56,938
Fine.

1040
00:57:58,884 --> 00:58:00,511
Keep it. Thank you so much.

1041
00:58:00,685 --> 00:58:02,516
You're so kind.
- Thank you.

1042
00:58:02,687 --> 00:58:05,247
Take care. ''Go...go...go...Govinda.''

1043
00:58:14,699 --> 00:58:17,497
Papa!
- Sushila.

1044
00:58:17,936 --> 00:58:19,233
ls everything fine?

1045
00:58:20,272 --> 00:58:21,864
Go up and take a look in
the house, you'll know.

1046
00:58:22,574 --> 00:58:23,973
Thankfully we survived, otherwise..

1047
00:58:24,309 --> 00:58:25,799
No, l'll talk to the police.

1048
00:58:25,877 --> 00:58:26,673
Don't worry.

1049
00:58:26,745 --> 00:58:31,478
They hurled stones and
acid bottles in our house.

1050
00:58:32,250 --> 00:58:34,275
l don't care lf l die.

1051
00:58:34,352 --> 00:58:35,376
But the children.

1052
00:58:36,354 --> 00:58:38,914
lf Jigna would've
been hit by that acid..

1053
00:58:38,990 --> 00:58:40,582
l won't let anything happen to them.

1054
00:58:40,659 --> 00:58:41,648
l am their father. Please.

1055
00:58:41,726 --> 00:58:43,318
So, understand the duties of a father.

1056
00:58:43,395 --> 00:58:45,295
Withdraw the case.
- You're a fool.

1057
00:58:45,964 --> 00:58:47,261
l'm about to lose my house.

1058
00:58:49,701 --> 00:58:50,895
Where will we stay?

1059
00:58:51,469 --> 00:58:53,767
On the streets, or in their house?

1060
00:58:54,840 --> 00:58:56,398
Do we have any other option?

1061
00:58:56,508 --> 00:58:57,406
Why don't you understand?

1062
00:58:57,509 --> 00:58:59,272
Come on, Jigna. Sit in the car.

1063
00:58:59,644 --> 00:59:01,771
Come.
- He's made a mess of things.

1064
00:59:01,847 --> 00:59:03,508
l won't leave papa.

1065
00:59:04,716 --> 00:59:06,240
l'll slap you if you refuse.
- No, mother.

1066
00:59:06,318 --> 00:59:08,218
Come on, sit inside.

1067
00:59:10,889 --> 00:59:11,913
Please..

1068
00:59:57,066 --> 00:59:58,124
Hello.

1069
00:59:59,001 --> 01:00:00,059
Hello.

1070
01:00:00,870 --> 01:00:02,770
Who is it?
- Bhagwan (God).

1071
01:00:02,972 --> 01:00:04,462
What?

1072
01:00:04,740 --> 01:00:06,970
lf you were a Muslim,
l would've said Allah.

1073
01:00:07,543 --> 01:00:09,568
lf you were a Christian,
then Jesus Christ.

1074
01:00:09,812 --> 01:00:12,212
You're a Hindu, so Krishna.

1075
01:00:18,087 --> 01:00:19,486
You, here?

1076
01:00:20,856 --> 01:00:24,155
You're an excellent stuntman, really.

1077
01:00:24,226 --> 01:00:25,056
Very good.

1078
01:00:25,127 --> 01:00:27,118
l'm sure you're
acting is decent as well.

1079
01:00:27,796 --> 01:00:30,629
Why don't you approach
some television channel?

1080
01:00:30,699 --> 01:00:35,159
They keep remaking
Ramayan and Mahabharat.

1081
01:00:35,738 --> 01:00:37,103
Krishna.

1082
01:00:38,908 --> 01:00:41,001
Suited-booted Krishna.

1083
01:00:41,610 --> 01:00:43,043
Here to teach me a lesson.

1084
01:00:44,480 --> 01:00:46,038
Look.

1085
01:00:46,615 --> 01:00:48,446
Look there.

1086
01:00:48,584 --> 01:00:50,484
Gods are bare-bodied.

1087
01:00:50,586 --> 01:00:51,814
Like this.

1088
01:00:52,454 --> 01:00:54,752
They're never fully covered.

1089
01:00:56,025 --> 01:00:57,754
That's your wedding photo, right?
- Yes.

1090
01:00:57,826 --> 01:00:59,054
Wearing that traditional attire.

1091
01:00:59,094 --> 01:01:01,494
So, did you only wear
a traditional attire..

1092
01:01:01,564 --> 01:01:02,724
..since your wedding?

1093
01:01:02,798 --> 01:01:04,163
No, right?
- No.

1094
01:01:04,700 --> 01:01:07,635
See. That's our older image.

1095
01:01:07,903 --> 01:01:10,098
Conch in one hand, mace in the other.

1096
01:01:10,172 --> 01:01:11,867
Where are yours?

1097
01:01:11,941 --> 01:01:15,001
lf l keep holding them all day,
won't my arms hurt?

1098
01:01:17,813 --> 01:01:18,973
Think.

1099
01:01:19,048 --> 01:01:21,846
Actually, our latest photos
haven't been updated on Facebook.

1100
01:01:22,484 --> 01:01:23,917
People still use the
older ones, and we let them.

1101
01:01:23,986 --> 01:01:24,953
We don't have a problem.

1102
01:01:25,020 --> 01:01:26,954
- Let them. - That's enough.

1103
01:01:27,156 --> 01:01:29,590
You're boring me now. Get out, leave.

1104
01:01:32,528 --> 01:01:33,893
Mahadev!

1105
01:01:34,697 --> 01:01:39,066
- Mahadev! - Only you
can hear and see me.

1106
01:01:39,535 --> 01:01:41,503
Yes, coming. Coming.

1107
01:01:45,941 --> 01:01:46,908
Mahadev!

1108
01:01:46,942 --> 01:01:48,432
What happened? What happened, Kanji?

1109
01:01:48,978 --> 01:01:49,876
See him.

1110
01:01:49,912 --> 01:01:51,777
He calls himself God.

1111
01:01:52,681 --> 01:01:53,807
l can see him.

1112
01:01:54,049 --> 01:01:55,448
He can see you.

1113
01:01:55,517 --> 01:01:58,486
My name's Krishna, your new neighbour.

1114
01:01:59,154 --> 01:02:00,644
Neighbour?

1115
01:02:01,457 --> 01:02:02,617
Neighbour?

1116
01:02:02,658 --> 01:02:04,990
The person Kanji had
mortgaged his house to..

1117
01:02:05,060 --> 01:02:06,584
..has sold it to me.

1118
01:02:07,963 --> 01:02:09,157
Here are the documents.

1119
01:02:12,601 --> 01:02:16,093
And, Kanji bhai, sorry
for that joke about God.

1120
01:02:18,107 --> 01:02:19,574
What's this?

1121
01:02:19,908 --> 01:02:22,035
How can he sell my house to him?

1122
01:02:22,111 --> 01:02:23,976
l was about to pay him on time.

1123
01:02:24,046 --> 01:02:25,035
l already paid him.

1124
01:02:25,080 --> 01:02:26,479
This isn't done.

1125
01:02:26,582 --> 01:02:27,742
This is my house.
Nobody can just buy it.

1126
01:02:27,816 --> 01:02:30,148
Relax. Chill.

1127
01:02:30,753 --> 01:02:33,813
When you get your
compensation from God..

1128
01:02:33,889 --> 01:02:37,757
..you can repay me, l will leave.

1129
01:02:37,793 --> 01:02:40,785
And anyway, l always leave
after my project is over.

1130
01:02:40,863 --> 01:02:44,094
Why buy the house
when you want to leave?

1131
01:02:44,633 --> 01:02:45,725
Are you a agent?

1132
01:02:47,703 --> 01:02:49,102
l am not that low.

1133
01:02:49,505 --> 01:02:50,836
l've a consultancy firm.

1134
01:02:51,440 --> 01:02:53,533
l give advice to people.
- Advice.

1135
01:02:53,609 --> 01:02:55,600
Anyone who thinks of me.

1136
01:02:55,678 --> 01:02:57,475
Public service. Service open to all.

1137
01:02:57,913 --> 01:03:00,074
A solution to every problem.

1138
01:03:00,749 --> 01:03:03,115
Sometimes it gets slightly delayed.

1139
01:03:03,185 --> 01:03:04,982
But...l always get there on time.

1140
01:03:05,521 --> 01:03:06,818
There's delay but not denial.

1141
01:03:06,889 --> 01:03:09,016
Just like l came here,
to help Kanji bhai.

1142
01:03:09,692 --> 01:03:10,716
Help me?

1143
01:03:10,793 --> 01:03:12,055
l found out about your condition..

1144
01:03:12,127 --> 01:03:13,754
..only after l brought the house.

1145
01:03:14,763 --> 01:03:15,889
The court case, lost your shop..

1146
01:03:15,964 --> 01:03:17,158
..and your wife and children too.

1147
01:03:17,466 --> 01:03:19,491
Kanji bhai, don't worry.

1148
01:03:19,702 --> 01:03:20,930
You can stay here.

1149
01:03:21,804 --> 01:03:24,534
ln return,
l will only use your things.

1150
01:03:24,673 --> 01:03:26,470
Television, fridge, etcetera.

1151
01:03:30,179 --> 01:03:31,476
Fine, but remember..

1152
01:03:31,547 --> 01:03:33,606
..one day l will buy this
house back from you.

1153
01:03:33,749 --> 01:03:34,875
So be it!

1154
01:03:35,584 --> 01:03:37,074
l mean, l promise.

1155
01:03:38,620 --> 01:03:40,588
He's a nice man.
- Something you said.

1156
01:03:40,656 --> 01:03:42,624
No, just.. Cheers.

1157
01:03:44,426 --> 01:03:45,484
Calls himself God.

1158
01:03:45,561 --> 01:03:46,550
l think he's drunk.

1159
01:03:46,628 --> 01:03:50,689
Thank you, for letting
me stay in my own house.

1160
01:03:50,933 --> 01:03:52,423
Thank you so much.

1161
01:03:53,602 --> 01:03:54,762
Thank you.

1162
01:03:55,938 --> 01:03:58,498
l will sleep outside on the terrace.

1163
01:03:58,874 --> 01:04:00,466
And you can sleep wherever you want.

1164
01:04:00,509 --> 01:04:01,533
lt's your house.

1165
01:04:01,844 --> 01:04:03,471
Thank you. Goodnight.

1166
01:04:03,779 --> 01:04:05,838
And yes, the light
switch is at the back.

1167
01:04:05,948 --> 01:04:07,609
Switch off the lights
before you go to sleep.

1168
01:04:12,187 --> 01:04:13,677
Another power failure.

1169
01:04:14,990 --> 01:04:19,051
No. you switched it off.
- No, l didn't.

1170
01:04:19,128 --> 01:04:20,186
You're drunk.

1171
01:04:20,462 --> 01:04:21,622
So?

1172
01:04:23,932 --> 01:04:25,160
l see.

1173
01:04:36,478 --> 01:04:39,003
''Go...go...go...Govinda.''

1174
01:04:43,585 --> 01:04:46,145
''Go...go...go...Govinda.''

1175
01:04:50,826 --> 01:04:52,987
''Go...go...go...Govinda.''

1176
01:05:17,519 --> 01:05:19,987
Case on God admitted. Paper,
paper, paper.

1177
01:05:20,055 --> 01:05:21,784
High Court has put it's seal on it.

1178
01:05:28,497 --> 01:05:31,022
Through the notice prepared
by advocate Hanif Qureshi..

1179
01:05:31,099 --> 01:05:33,897
..Kanji Lalji Mehta's case
on God has been accepted.

1180
01:05:34,002 --> 01:05:35,094
l think he's mad.

1181
01:05:35,170 --> 01:05:36,501
Who is this guy?

1182
01:05:36,538 --> 01:05:37,630
Hey Jigna, what happened?

1183
01:05:44,079 --> 01:05:46,138
See, his wife ran away.

1184
01:05:46,515 --> 01:05:47,982
Who can live with that madman?

1185
01:05:48,050 --> 01:05:50,450
l don't even talk to him.

1186
01:05:50,485 --> 01:05:52,476
Or the Lord might punish us as well.

1187
01:05:57,459 --> 01:06:00,121
What a splendid bike.
- But, who is he?

1188
01:06:00,495 --> 01:06:02,019
l think he arrived just last night.

1189
01:06:04,132 --> 01:06:07,067
Who's playing this classical music?

1190
01:06:07,169 --> 01:06:11,799
l've heard that the new
guest is really handsome.

1191
01:06:11,874 --> 01:06:13,842
Don't l look handsome?

1192
01:06:14,576 --> 01:06:15,668
Get inside.

1193
01:06:22,751 --> 01:06:24,184
Hey, Hari Prasad.

1194
01:06:26,655 --> 01:06:27,952
Hey, Chaurasiya.

1195
01:06:28,690 --> 01:06:30,487
What's all this?

1196
01:06:31,026 --> 01:06:32,493
l was waking up the birds!

1197
01:06:32,527 --> 01:06:33,687
What? Who?

1198
01:06:33,762 --> 01:06:35,457
l was waking up the birds!

1199
01:06:35,731 --> 01:06:37,562
Practice. l was practising.

1200
01:06:37,900 --> 01:06:39,197
lt's a good thing to
do in the morning.

1201
01:06:39,501 --> 01:06:41,628
Don't do it.
Don't do all this in my house.

1202
01:06:43,839 --> 01:06:45,773
lt's your house you can
play anything you want.

1203
01:06:46,441 --> 01:06:47,999
Good morning.
- What?

1204
01:06:48,110 --> 01:06:50,442
Not me, there's a lady in your house.

1205
01:06:51,546 --> 01:06:52,706
Hello.

1206
01:06:53,448 --> 01:06:54,574
Hello.

1207
01:06:54,616 --> 01:06:56,777
l brought breakfast.

1208
01:06:56,852 --> 01:06:58,979
l thought since sister-in-law isn't home,
so.. - No need.

1209
01:06:59,054 --> 01:07:00,749
l'll have bread and butter.

1210
01:07:03,158 --> 01:07:04,682
Where's the butter?

1211
01:07:05,594 --> 01:07:06,720
l ate it.

1212
01:07:09,965 --> 01:07:12,729
There was half a kilo of
butter in there, you ate it all.

1213
01:07:12,801 --> 01:07:14,962
lt's my favourite thing. So l ate it.

1214
01:07:15,137 --> 01:07:16,570
Tell me one thing.

1215
01:07:16,638 --> 01:07:18,538
Why do they make it so salty?

1216
01:07:19,041 --> 01:07:20,599
Just like his name.

1217
01:07:21,944 --> 01:07:23,070
Are you all alone?

1218
01:07:23,145 --> 01:07:24,840
Your wife?
- Of course.

1219
01:07:25,013 --> 01:07:26,480
Sixteen thousand..
- What?

1220
01:07:26,515 --> 01:07:27,539
She lives in Sholapur.

1221
01:07:29,184 --> 01:07:31,744
What did you hear?
- Sixteen thousand.

1222
01:07:32,054 --> 01:07:34,579
No, she lives in Sholapur.

1223
01:07:34,823 --> 01:07:36,188
He can't handle one..

1224
01:07:36,491 --> 01:07:37,924
..how can l have sixteen thousand.

1225
01:07:37,993 --> 01:07:40,188
Please go. He's a big liar.

1226
01:07:40,495 --> 01:07:41,621
He was boring me yesterday.

1227
01:07:41,697 --> 01:07:43,927
- Please go.
- Give it.

1228
01:07:46,001 --> 01:07:47,969
lf you eat all that
you'll get a stomach ache.

1229
01:07:48,036 --> 01:07:49,731
First half a kilo of
butter and now this.

1230
01:07:50,138 --> 01:07:51,628
l'll be fine.

1231
01:07:54,509 --> 01:07:56,773
- Hello.
- Sir, l'm speaking from ABP News.

1232
01:07:56,878 --> 01:07:58,778
l am standing below your house.

1233
01:07:59,982 --> 01:08:01,415
Sir.

1234
01:08:01,683 --> 01:08:04,584
Look, l don't want to be
a piece of news for you.

1235
01:08:05,087 --> 01:08:06,952
And don't call me again.

1236
01:08:07,656 --> 01:08:09,556
Sir, just one interview.

1237
01:08:09,758 --> 01:08:14,661
Since he filed a case
against God, he's become alone.

1238
01:08:17,032 --> 01:08:18,761
One has to tread on such a path alone.

1239
01:08:19,901 --> 01:08:22,802
Let's see how far our friend goes.

1240
01:08:26,041 --> 01:08:27,702
The advocate who
prepared Kanji's notice.

1241
01:08:27,776 --> 01:08:29,471
He lives that way.

1242
01:08:29,511 --> 01:08:31,479
Excuse me, advocate Hanif Qureshi.

1243
01:08:31,780 --> 01:08:33,077
He lives right there.

1244
01:08:33,148 --> 01:08:35,639
Where does advocate
Hanif Qureshi live?

1245
01:08:35,717 --> 01:08:37,048
He lives right there.

1246
01:08:37,452 --> 01:08:39,511
Advocate Hanif Qureshi lives there.

1247
01:08:45,827 --> 01:08:48,796
155 letters, and calls too.

1248
01:08:49,464 --> 01:08:52,797
Bhuj, Latur, Vishakapatnam.

1249
01:08:53,468 --> 01:08:56,437
Their claims haven't been approved..

1250
01:08:56,505 --> 01:08:59,668
..for the past few years due to
'Act of God'.

1251
01:09:00,842 --> 01:09:04,903
All they all want you
to defend their cases.

1252
01:09:05,881 --> 01:09:10,750
Son, l've lost my house
in the earthquake.

1253
01:09:12,654 --> 01:09:17,148
My son and his wife died too.

1254
01:09:21,530 --> 01:09:22,792
This is my grandson.

1255
01:09:23,532 --> 01:09:26,000
His cancer needs to be operated.

1256
01:09:26,668 --> 01:09:30,934
lf l get the insurance money,
everything will be alright.

1257
01:09:31,907 --> 01:09:33,738
This is Aslam.

1258
01:09:33,775 --> 01:09:34,969
Hello.
- Hello.

1259
01:09:35,043 --> 01:09:37,068
He lost everything in the Tsunami.

1260
01:09:37,913 --> 01:09:42,179
He lost all the money he had
saved for his sister's marriage.

1261
01:09:44,119 --> 01:09:45,552
So you file a case too.

1262
01:09:45,620 --> 01:09:47,019
l'll be cast out..

1263
01:09:47,089 --> 01:09:51,082
..if l go against the
priest or community.

1264
01:09:51,159 --> 01:09:53,684
Look, Aslam. You
aren't going against anyone.

1265
01:09:54,463 --> 01:09:58,661
Those who taught you religion,
taught you to pray..

1266
01:09:58,733 --> 01:10:03,033
..you're just questioning
them why Allah did this to you.

1267
01:10:04,005 --> 01:10:06,974
But, the priest..
- Aslam.

1268
01:10:07,576 --> 01:10:10,204
When you lose your home..

1269
01:10:10,979 --> 01:10:13,812
..will the priest let
you stay in his house?

1270
01:10:15,117 --> 01:10:19,577
Religion is for people,
people aren't made for religion.

1271
01:10:24,993 --> 01:10:29,123
Hanif, how long will it
take to ready their papers?

1272
01:10:29,798 --> 01:10:31,493
As long as it will take me to type.

1273
01:10:32,767 --> 01:10:34,098
Let's begin.

1274
01:10:55,824 --> 01:10:58,759
First one crore, and now
claims worth 400 crores.

1275
01:10:58,827 --> 01:11:00,021
Kanji Mehta!

1276
01:11:00,662 --> 01:11:02,152
Advocate Sardesai is caught between..

1277
01:11:02,464 --> 01:11:04,523
..the insurance company
and religious organizations.

1278
01:11:04,599 --> 01:11:06,897
For God's sake, prove that God exists.

1279
01:11:06,968 --> 01:11:09,095
And...and...make God pay all this!

1280
01:11:09,171 --> 01:11:12,663
The temples, mosques,
churches, they will pay everything.

1281
01:11:12,741 --> 01:11:13,935
Kanji.

1282
01:11:14,476 --> 01:11:16,137
Wasn't your fight with your God?

1283
01:11:16,211 --> 01:11:18,611
Silence please!
- So why call me here?

1284
01:11:18,847 --> 01:11:24,877
Priest, how can l say
which God of which religion..

1285
01:11:25,487 --> 01:11:28,854
..was behind this earthquake,
