01:40:03,970 --> 01:40:06,200
Or are you blindly agreeing..

1777
01:40:06,539 --> 01:40:08,507
..to whatever Leeladhar is saying.

1778
01:40:08,842 --> 01:40:11,106
Your Honour,
small children in school..

1779
01:40:11,177 --> 01:40:12,940
..don't remember the entire prayer.

1780
01:40:13,513 --> 01:40:15,481
So they just close their eyes and...

1781
01:40:15,515 --> 01:40:16,914
Move their lips.

1782
01:40:17,050 --> 01:40:18,847
They move their lips and
you're moving your hands.

1783
01:40:18,919 --> 01:40:20,477
Kanji.

1784
01:40:21,588 --> 01:40:25,820
You've insulted a learned sage.

1785
01:40:25,892 --> 01:40:28,588
So?
- You won't get refuge even in hell.

1786
01:40:28,962 --> 01:40:30,691
How can l?

1787
01:40:31,498 --> 01:40:34,228
You've already reserved places there.

1788
01:40:39,539 --> 01:40:41,530
How dare you?

1789
01:40:42,142 --> 01:40:43,575
How dare you?

1790
01:40:43,910 --> 01:40:46,003
Atheist!

1791
01:40:47,981 --> 01:40:49,573
Silence.
- Leave me! Leave me!

1792
01:40:49,649 --> 01:40:51,014
What are you doing?

1793
01:40:51,084 --> 01:40:54,019
This is the court, sit down.

1794
01:40:56,022 --> 01:40:58,582
Order, order.

1795
01:41:01,094 --> 01:41:02,527
Sit down everyone.

1796
01:41:21,848 --> 01:41:24,749
Chapter 2, verse 56.

1797
01:41:26,619 --> 01:41:32,717
Meaning, a person for whom
happiness and sorrows is equal..

1798
01:41:32,759 --> 01:41:38,220
..and is devoid of anger and fear,
and has a calm mind..

1799
01:41:38,531 --> 01:41:40,624
..is called a learned person.

1800
01:41:46,039 --> 01:41:47,870
They'll teach me Gita?

1801
01:41:48,141 --> 01:41:50,473
They can't teach me, Your Honour.

1802
01:41:50,543 --> 01:41:53,671
Their lQ is lower than
the room temperature.

1803
01:41:56,816 --> 01:42:00,775
l said a few things to instigate you..

1804
01:42:00,854 --> 01:42:02,151
..you tried to harm me.

1805
01:42:02,622 --> 01:42:05,489
ls this your achievement, Siddeshwar?

1806
01:42:05,558 --> 01:42:08,755
Mr. Kanji, the issue
isn't his achievement..

1807
01:42:08,828 --> 01:42:10,955
..the issue here is
who razed down your shop?

1808
01:42:11,498 --> 01:42:12,522
God did.

1809
01:42:12,599 --> 01:42:13,497
You're giving a verdict.

1810
01:42:13,566 --> 01:42:15,659
That's the judge's duty.

1811
01:42:16,102 --> 01:42:18,002
You just have to prove..

1812
01:42:18,071 --> 01:42:20,539
..that God caused that earthquake.

1813
01:42:20,607 --> 01:42:21,733
Yes, and it's
impossible to prove that.

1814
01:42:21,808 --> 01:42:23,139
Relax, relax, relax.

1815
01:42:23,209 --> 01:42:24,938
Nothing is impossible.

1816
01:42:26,646 --> 01:42:29,911
Tell me one thing.

1817
01:42:30,250 --> 01:42:33,981
The Lord has narrated
the 'Bhagvad Gita'. - Yes.

1818
01:42:34,054 --> 01:42:37,148
And everything said in
the 'Bhagvad Gita' is true.

1819
01:42:37,991 --> 01:42:39,117
Absolutely.

1820
01:42:39,526 --> 01:42:40,857
Point to be noted, Your Honour.

1821
01:42:41,094 --> 01:42:45,087
So tell me, why did God say in the
eight verse of the ninth chapter..

1822
01:42:45,165 --> 01:42:50,432
..of the 'Gita',
''l've created the entire universe..''

1823
01:42:50,703 --> 01:42:53,001
''..and it will be
destroyed on my will''.

1824
01:42:53,073 --> 01:42:55,735
''The entire creation follows my will.''

1825
01:42:56,176 --> 01:42:59,737
''lt is only l, who is responsible..

1826
01:42:59,813 --> 01:43:01,747
..for its creation
and its destruction.''

1827
01:43:02,882 --> 01:43:04,543
And look.

1828
01:43:04,617 --> 01:43:06,915
Your Honour, it's been
said in the Bible as well.

1829
01:43:08,121 --> 01:43:10,954
Chapter 54, verse 16.

1830
01:43:13,093 --> 01:43:16,551
''See, it is l who have
created the smith..''

1831
01:43:16,629 --> 01:43:19,655
''..who blows the fire of coals
and produces a weapon..''

1832
01:43:19,732 --> 01:43:21,029
''..fit for his purpose.''

1833
01:43:21,568 --> 01:43:25,561
''l've also created the
ravager to destroy.''

1834
01:43:26,139 --> 01:43:27,538
And see this.

1835
01:43:27,607 --> 01:43:28,972
Also in the Holy Quran.

1836
01:43:29,642 --> 01:43:33,203
Sur-e-Zalzala 99,
verse 108 states that..

1837
01:43:33,713 --> 01:43:37,581
''..the entire earth will
be shaken to its core.''

1838
01:43:37,750 --> 01:43:41,516
''And the earth will
spill out its burden.''

1839
01:43:41,654 --> 01:43:44,452
''And humans will question,
what's happening.''

1840
01:43:44,691 --> 01:43:48,058
''And that day,
she will unveil her plight.''

1841
01:43:48,461 --> 01:43:52,898
''Because the Lord would've
ordered her to do so.''

1842
01:43:53,032 --> 01:43:54,590
''The Lord.''

1843
01:44:01,774 --> 01:44:04,641
All these things mean the same thing..

1844
01:44:05,745 --> 01:44:07,906
..that my shop was razed down..

1845
01:44:07,947 --> 01:44:10,472
..due to the earthquake caused by God.

1846
01:44:10,550 --> 01:44:13,041
That means it is an act of God.

1847
01:44:13,653 --> 01:44:15,518
lt's His doing.

1848
01:44:16,055 --> 01:44:18,683
And, all those who
have suffered losses..

1849
01:44:18,758 --> 01:44:23,457
..due to Him, will have
to be compensated by God.

1850
01:44:27,100 --> 01:44:29,159
Otherwise, their collection agents.

1851
01:44:33,673 --> 01:44:35,504
Your Honour, Mr. Kanji is
trying to confuse Leeladhar..

1852
01:44:35,575 --> 01:44:36,633
..with his words.

1853
01:44:36,709 --> 01:44:37,869
Mr. Sardesai.

1854
01:44:38,778 --> 01:44:40,871
What are you doing? Let him speak.

1855
01:44:41,047 --> 01:44:43,072
lf it's proven that God exists..

1856
01:44:43,516 --> 01:44:44,983
..then we won't have to pay.

1857
01:44:45,018 --> 01:44:46,508
l see.

1858
01:44:47,153 --> 01:44:49,917
- Now you want to blame us completely.
- Be quiet.

1859
01:44:49,989 --> 01:44:52,981
- You cannot blame the Lord
to hide your sins. - Be quiet.

1860
01:44:53,092 --> 01:44:55,720
Because only we have
a copyright on God.

1861
01:44:55,795 --> 01:44:57,126
Copyright?

1862
01:44:57,430 --> 01:44:58,920
Just because you constructed
a few temples.. - Silence.

1863
01:44:58,998 --> 01:45:00,522
..you think God belongs to you..

1864
01:45:00,900 --> 01:45:02,162
Beware.

1865
01:45:02,468 --> 01:45:04,129
Our community won't spare you.

1866
01:45:04,437 --> 01:45:05,631
What's he..
- Silence!

1867
01:45:05,672 --> 01:45:06,934
Relax.

1868
01:45:08,608 --> 01:45:13,011
Until today l had heard
that God is venerated..

1869
01:45:13,079 --> 01:45:15,877
..He is worshipped, prayed to.

1870
01:45:16,149 --> 01:45:20,142
But now l see that
Gods have copyrights too.

1871
01:45:23,056 --> 01:45:24,751
God's copyright?

1872
01:45:24,824 --> 01:45:27,452
These people have
turned God into a brand.

1873
01:45:28,828 --> 01:45:33,026
Now l am assured
that God doesn't exist.

1874
01:45:33,800 --> 01:45:35,028
Not possible.

1875
01:45:35,168 --> 01:45:37,466
Because if He really existed..

1876
01:45:37,537 --> 01:45:40,768
..he would've rid
the world of imposters like you.

1877
01:45:41,674 --> 01:45:45,110
l've already proven what
l wanted to, Your Honour.

1878
01:45:45,878 --> 01:45:47,846
Now the verdict..

1879
01:45:54,153 --> 01:45:55,984
Mr. Kanji, are you alright?

1880
01:45:56,923 --> 01:46:00,120
Mr. kanji, are you alright?

1881
01:46:01,527 --> 01:46:02,516
Mr. Kanji.

1882
01:46:02,595 --> 01:46:04,153
Kanji bhai! Kanji bhai!

1883
01:46:04,430 --> 01:46:05,897
Kanji bhai! Kanji bhai!

1884
01:46:05,965 --> 01:46:08,024
What's wrong with my brother?

1885
01:46:08,101 --> 01:46:09,898
Someone get water.

1886
01:46:10,436 --> 01:46:12,028
Kanji bhai! Kanji bhai!

1887
01:46:13,439 --> 01:46:14,497
Thank you.
- Call the ambulance.

1888
01:46:14,574 --> 01:46:15,802
Call the ambulance.

1889
01:46:24,550 --> 01:46:26,108
Yes, he's here.

1890
01:46:26,185 --> 01:46:27,584
Excuse me.
- Just a minute, just a minute.

1891
01:46:27,654 --> 01:46:30,919
Let me thought.
- Please let us pass.

1892
01:46:31,090 --> 01:46:32,955
You cannot go inside.
- No, no, no.

1893
01:46:33,026 --> 01:46:35,460
Please, l said you cannot..
- But he's my husband.

1894
01:46:35,495 --> 01:46:36,689
l want to see him.

1895
01:46:39,499 --> 01:46:42,229
Doctor, is he alright?

1896
01:46:42,935 --> 01:46:44,562
lt's a severe attack of paralysis.

1897
01:46:44,837 --> 01:46:46,065
And now he's gone into coma.

1898
01:47:06,059 --> 01:47:08,118
He's on ventilator and..

1899
01:47:08,461 --> 01:47:10,053
..only God can save him now.

1900
01:47:23,476 --> 01:47:25,671
The 400 crore in
compensations under the 'Act of God'..

1901
01:47:25,745 --> 01:47:27,144
..will now be paid out.

1902
01:47:30,817 --> 01:47:33,115
Great, Lord.

1903
01:48:22,468 --> 01:48:23,799
Where am l?

1904
01:48:24,904 --> 01:48:26,030
Don't say that.

1905
01:48:29,108 --> 01:48:30,507
You're in the lCU.

1906
01:48:30,910 --> 01:48:32,605
Your wife and children are outside.

1907
01:48:33,646 --> 01:48:35,477
No one's allowed inside.

1908
01:48:37,116 --> 01:48:38,549
Then how did you come in?

1909
01:48:40,920 --> 01:48:42,444
l came here to wake you up.

1910
01:48:45,491 --> 01:48:47,425
lt's time for you to get up.

1911
01:48:53,900 --> 01:48:55,959
You cussed God from your heart.

1912
01:48:57,937 --> 01:48:59,495
And where's the heart?

1913
01:48:59,906 --> 01:49:01,396
On your left.

1914
01:49:01,874 --> 01:49:05,139
So God has paralysed
your entire left side.

1915
01:49:07,513 --> 01:49:10,004
l am not saying this..

1916
01:49:11,451 --> 01:49:15,012
..it's the media outside
spreading this rumour.

1917
01:49:16,122 --> 01:49:19,523
l can cure you if you want.

1918
01:49:20,593 --> 01:49:22,458
So, you're a doctor now.

1919
01:49:23,029 --> 01:49:24,553
l am all in one.

1920
01:49:25,431 --> 01:49:27,160
Want to see a miracle.

1921
01:49:29,469 --> 01:49:35,169
Soaring around on
the bike isn't called miracle.

1922
01:49:35,508 --> 01:49:36,634
l see.

1923
01:49:38,711 --> 01:49:40,110
Here we go.

1924
01:50:27,226 --> 01:50:30,855
Krishna Vasudev Yadav, from Gokul.

1925
01:50:34,800 --> 01:50:36,165
Do you believe now?

1926
01:50:44,577 --> 01:50:47,774
''You're my mother, and my father.''

1927
01:50:48,014 --> 01:50:51,472
''You're my friend, and my companion.''

1928
01:50:51,851 --> 01:50:54,979
l've donned the same
form you always see..

1929
01:50:55,054 --> 01:50:58,490
..on televisions, calendars, movies.

1930
01:50:58,758 --> 01:51:00,817
l've been seen in this form for ages.

1931
01:51:00,893 --> 01:51:02,724
And l'm standing before
you in that same form.

1932
01:51:05,531 --> 01:51:09,023
But Kanji bhai, l'm not like that.

1933
01:51:11,470 --> 01:51:12,869
You really..

1934
01:51:14,006 --> 01:51:16,998
Forgive me, forgive me.

1935
01:51:17,977 --> 01:51:20,969
Just like a devotee is
incomplete without his God..

1936
01:51:22,114 --> 01:51:27,575
..similarly, God is incomplete
without his true devotee.

1937
01:51:33,826 --> 01:51:36,226
Why didn't you show me
this miracle before?

1938
01:51:38,931 --> 01:51:40,159
That's the problem.

1939
01:51:43,169 --> 01:51:44,636
Friend.

1940
01:51:45,638 --> 01:51:48,004
l am Krishna,
that's why l perform miracles.

1941
01:51:49,508 --> 01:51:53,103
l'm not Krishna,
because l perform miracles.

1942
01:51:54,814 --> 01:51:56,543
That means you're real.

1943
01:51:56,949 --> 01:51:58,177
God exists.

1944
01:51:58,784 --> 01:52:02,686
And God isn't my father-figure,
he's my friend.

1945
01:52:02,755 --> 01:52:07,954
l am everyone's friend,
but no one understands me one.

1946
01:52:08,027 --> 01:52:09,858
People gave you a high position.

1947
01:52:10,096 --> 01:52:11,723
And you staggered.

1948
01:52:12,531 --> 01:52:15,500
Yes, but l am not
like people think of me.

1949
01:52:16,636 --> 01:52:18,126
l've common sense too.

1950
01:52:19,038 --> 01:52:24,032
l am not interested
in people's offerings.

1951
01:52:24,477 --> 01:52:27,503
l want them to
distribute all this to the poor.

1952
01:52:28,080 --> 01:52:32,881
All l care about is their faith,
their love, their belief.

1953
01:52:32,952 --> 01:52:34,544
Just a minute.

1954
01:52:34,987 --> 01:52:36,215
Belief?

1955
01:52:36,622 --> 01:52:38,487
But l never believed in You.

1956
01:52:38,891 --> 01:52:40,222
l was an atheist.

1957
01:52:40,860 --> 01:52:42,088
Why did You show yourself to only me?

1958
01:52:43,462 --> 01:52:44,588
Kanji bhai, sit down.

1959
01:52:51,937 --> 01:52:53,427
Do you know what atheist means?

1960
01:52:55,508 --> 01:52:58,068
Someone who examines, thinks,
understands..

1961
01:52:58,144 --> 01:52:59,771
..and says that this is wrong.

1962
01:53:00,146 --> 01:53:01,443
The Lord doesn't exist.

1963
01:53:01,480 --> 01:53:03,641
He's an atheist.

1964
01:53:03,883 --> 01:53:05,441
That's why l appeared before you.

1965
01:53:05,985 --> 01:53:08,886
Because you did
everything a true atheist does.

1966
01:53:09,121 --> 01:53:12,750
And a true atheist can
become a real believer.

1967
01:53:13,492 --> 01:53:15,926
People come to me for
their own self-interest.

1968
01:53:16,729 --> 01:53:18,924
They come with
different exchange offers.

1969
01:53:19,165 --> 01:53:20,598
Exchange offer?

1970
01:53:21,133 --> 01:53:22,998
''Lord, if l pass my SSC exams..''

1971
01:53:23,069 --> 01:53:25,037
''..l will walk to
Siddhivinayak for 5 Tuesdays.''

1972
01:53:26,572 --> 01:53:30,633
''lf Dominic's agrees to marry me..''

1973
01:53:31,143 --> 01:53:34,476
''..l will light 11 candles
at Mt. Mary.''

1974
01:53:35,014 --> 01:53:37,812
''lf my wife gets pregnant..''

1975
01:53:38,017 --> 01:53:40,485
''..then l will come and
offer a blanket at your shrine.''

1976
01:53:40,986 --> 01:53:42,476
Different offers.

1977
01:53:43,089 --> 01:53:46,991
And those who can't blame me for it.

1978
01:53:47,626 --> 01:53:49,526
They say, we couldn't go there..

1979
01:53:49,628 --> 01:53:51,152
..because the Lord didn't call us.

1980
01:53:52,164 --> 01:53:53,893
The Lord didn't call?

1981
01:53:53,933 --> 01:53:54,865
Do they need a invitation card..
- Yes.

1982
01:53:54,934 --> 01:53:56,799
Do you want me to write
you an invitation card?

1983
01:53:57,069 --> 01:53:58,934
Don't l have anything better to do?

1984
01:53:59,638 --> 01:54:02,505
And anyway, Kanji bhai,
l am present in every element.

1985
01:54:02,842 --> 01:54:04,002
l am omnipresent.

1986
01:54:04,076 --> 01:54:05,668
lf you're present everywhere..

1987
01:54:05,711 --> 01:54:07,178
..why have they built temples?

1988
01:54:07,446 --> 01:54:09,175
l've my own house.

1989
01:54:09,782 --> 01:54:11,875
l don't want to live
inside those four walls.

1990
01:54:12,051 --> 01:54:14,952
Then? Why did you
create such a religion?

1991
01:54:15,454 --> 01:54:17,649
l only created humans.

1992
01:54:17,723 --> 01:54:20,817
And humans started religion, caste.

1993
01:54:20,893 --> 01:54:22,952
And it's been going on for years now..

1994
01:54:23,028 --> 01:54:25,462
..because you need it.

1995
01:54:25,531 --> 01:54:27,624
But one should
discard such a religion.

1996
01:54:29,034 --> 01:54:31,628
Never snatch the
religion from the people.

1997
01:54:32,004 --> 01:54:36,839
lf you take them away, they
will make you their religion.

1998
01:54:38,911 --> 01:54:40,538
You don't believe it, do you?

1999
01:54:44,116 --> 01:54:46,084
You've been in coma for a month.

2000
01:54:48,020 --> 01:54:49,647
Let me show you what has happened..

2001
01:54:49,722 --> 01:54:51,417
..in the past one month.

2002
01:54:52,491 --> 01:54:58,020
Kanji Prabhu paid me
a visit in my dreams yesterday.

2003
01:54:58,097 --> 01:55:03,729
And he said he's
the 11th Avatar of Lord Vishnu.

2004
01:55:03,803 --> 01:55:05,464
What's going on?

2005
01:55:06,505 --> 01:55:09,906
Kanji Prabhu appeared
in his four-armed form.

2006
01:55:10,776 --> 01:55:14,109
Holding the mace, the conch..

2007
01:55:15,581 --> 01:55:17,446
People all around the world..

2008
01:55:17,483 --> 01:55:19,178
..are seeing signs
of Kanji's Godly form.

2009
01:55:19,451 --> 01:55:20,918
l was on night duty.

2010
01:55:20,986 --> 01:55:22,715
A just closed my eyes.

2011
01:55:22,788 --> 01:55:25,154
And someone slapped me.

2012
01:55:25,457 --> 01:55:28,722
And that's when l heard a voice,
''No sleeping on duty''.

2013
01:55:28,794 --> 01:55:31,888
Circulate a few miraculous
stories of Kanji in the market..

2014
01:55:32,031 --> 01:55:33,794
..and people will
spread it like wildfire.

2015
01:55:34,500 --> 01:55:38,630
l had seen Kanji Prabhu
flying with his scooter.

2016
01:55:38,737 --> 01:55:40,466
He appeared suddenly.

2017
01:55:40,539 --> 01:55:42,598
10 feet, 15 feet, 20 feet.

2018
01:55:42,675 --> 01:55:44,142
Brother Kanji is God.

2019
01:55:44,410 --> 01:55:45,741
He is God.

2020
01:55:46,478 --> 01:55:49,106
The 'dharma gurus' have accepted
Kanji bhai's Kalki avatar..

2021
01:55:49,415 --> 01:55:51,406
..asked for an apology
and have decided..

2022
01:55:51,483 --> 01:55:53,974
..to pay the claims worth 400 crore.

2023
01:55:54,520 --> 01:55:58,456
lt was His will that we
should pay, so we did.

2024
01:55:58,524 --> 01:56:00,116
But why are you making him God?

2025
01:56:00,426 --> 01:56:01,825
Who told you that he is God?

2026
01:56:01,861 --> 01:56:05,854
Do you know...when you will die?

2027
01:56:06,799 --> 01:56:08,528
Do you?
- No.

2028
01:56:08,968 --> 01:56:10,765
l don't know either.

2029
01:56:12,071 --> 01:56:16,838
But he has decided his death day.

2030
01:56:19,178 --> 01:56:22,147
On 16th December as soon as
we switch off the ventilator..

2031
01:56:22,448 --> 01:56:23,813
..Kanji's story will be over.

2032
01:56:24,450 --> 01:56:26,645
But this time we've
incurred heavy losses.

2033
01:56:27,086 --> 01:56:28,917
400 crores in insurance claims.

2034
01:56:28,988 --> 01:56:30,148
One crore to the doctor.

2035
01:56:30,456 --> 01:56:32,151
And the expense to
construct the temple.

2036
01:56:32,458 --> 01:56:34,517
lt's a onetime investment, Mr. Mishra.

2037
01:56:34,627 --> 01:56:36,754
We'll recover it in a year.

2038
01:56:36,996 --> 01:56:42,457
And anyway, we haven't had
a new God for a long time now.

2039
01:56:46,505 --> 01:56:49,997
''Hail Lord Kanji Wala.''

2040
01:56:50,609 --> 01:56:54,841
''Hail Lord Kanji Wala.''

2041
01:56:55,147 --> 01:56:59,641
''Om Lord Kanji Wala.''

2042
01:57:00,619 --> 01:57:05,147
''Sugar's high,
feeling breathless too.''

2043
01:57:05,457 --> 01:57:09,723
''Cure my swine flu.''
- Cure my swine flu.

2044
01:57:10,763 --> 01:57:13,664
l am going.
- Mahadev, wait.

2045
01:57:13,732 --> 01:57:15,529
Where are you going so hastily?

2046
01:57:15,634 --> 01:57:16,931
Forsake your anger.

2047
01:57:17,536 --> 01:57:20,061
The bed besides Kanji bhai is empty.

2048
01:57:21,507 --> 01:57:22,906
Do you want me to
reserve that for you?

2049
01:57:22,975 --> 01:57:28,140
He will forsake his
body on his birthday.

2050
01:57:30,115 --> 01:57:35,678
His shrine will be built
right where his shop was.

2051
01:57:35,754 --> 01:57:37,949
That isn't all. Now watch this.

2052
01:57:38,457 --> 01:57:41,051
All arrangements to transport
Kanji bhai's tomb has been made.

2053
01:57:41,126 --> 01:57:42,889
You snatched their business..

2054
01:57:42,962 --> 01:57:45,089
..and they made you their business.

2055
01:57:45,731 --> 01:57:46,629
Yes.

2056
01:57:46,699 --> 01:57:49,725
Kanji bhai, they've made an estimate..

2057
01:57:49,802 --> 01:57:54,466
..to earn 450 crores from your temple.

2058
01:57:54,807 --> 01:57:57,605
You're God, you
should've stopped them.

2059
01:57:57,676 --> 01:58:00,509
Friend, l would've ended the
battle of Mahabharat in a second..

2060
01:58:00,579 --> 01:58:01,807
..if l had picked up the weapon.

2061
01:58:01,880 --> 01:58:03,541
But that isn't my job.

2062
01:58:03,615 --> 01:58:06,675
My job is to show
people right and wrong.

2063
01:58:06,752 --> 01:58:08,652
This is your temple, your battle.

2064
01:58:08,721 --> 01:58:10,780
You decide what you should do.

2065
01:58:10,856 --> 01:58:15,088
Fight if you want to, or stay quiet.

2066
01:58:25,537 --> 01:58:26,936
Save him, please doctor.

2067
01:58:27,006 --> 01:58:28,803
We cannot do anything now.

2068
01:58:29,475 --> 01:58:31,943
And anyway, it's his last wish.

2069
01:58:32,011 --> 01:58:34,479
He is God.

2070
01:58:36,015 --> 01:58:37,448
Just a minute.

2071
01:58:37,516 --> 01:58:40,451
Wait here,
we'll bring the dead body out.

2072
01:58:46,525 --> 01:58:50,962
Donate as much as you wish in the donation
box kept in front of Kanji Prabhu..

2073
01:58:51,030 --> 01:58:53,624
..and have your wishes fulfilled.

2074
01:58:53,866 --> 01:58:57,063
The rate for VlP line is Rs. 101.

2075
01:58:57,136 --> 01:58:59,866
Welcome, welcome, Mahadev.

2076
01:59:00,939 --> 01:59:04,568
Swami, our very own Mahadeveshwar.

2077
01:59:05,010 --> 01:59:06,875
This is called destiny.

2078
01:59:06,945 --> 01:59:12,008
Kanji's chapter's going to
end right where it started.

2079
01:59:23,095 --> 01:59:25,586
Kanji bhai's body has gone
missing from the hospital.

2080
01:59:25,898 --> 01:59:29,026
The hospital
administration has no explanation.

2081
01:59:29,601 --> 01:59:32,502
Offerings made in
clarified butter, only Rs.25.

2082
01:59:32,604 --> 01:59:34,731
Where did Kanji disappear to?

2083
01:59:36,809 --> 01:59:39,039
Call Mr. Mishra.

2084
01:59:40,612 --> 01:59:41,636
There he is.

2085
01:59:41,713 --> 01:59:43,874
He isn't Spiderman. Find him.

2086
01:59:45,117 --> 01:59:47,847
l just found out. Don't worry.

2087
01:59:47,920 --> 01:59:50,445
l am there. l'll do something.

2088
01:59:50,789 --> 01:59:56,625
Kanji Prabhu's dead body can arrive
in the truck anytime now. - Go on.

2089
01:59:56,762 --> 02:00:02,530
Everyone please keep calm, everyone
will get a chance to behold him.

2090
02:00:03,502 --> 02:00:05,800
photographs of Sri Kanji Prabhu.

2091
02:00:05,871 --> 02:00:09,068
Kanji Prabhu's autobiography.

2092
02:00:21,954 --> 02:00:24,218
You are a fool.

2093
02:00:24,523 --> 02:00:25,956
l gave orders and you
set out to look for Kanji.

2094
02:00:26,024 --> 02:00:27,855
Who do you think he is?

2095
02:00:28,494 --> 02:00:30,018
Let's get out of here quietly,
otherwise..

2096
02:00:30,095 --> 02:00:31,528
..the people won't spare us.

2097
02:00:31,597 --> 02:00:33,258
Come on.

2098
02:00:53,452 --> 02:00:55,477
Kanji is alive.

2099
02:00:58,690 --> 02:01:00,590
Yes, l am alive.

2100
02:01:05,531 --> 02:01:07,089
What are you staring at?

2101
02:01:07,599 --> 02:01:11,831
l am the same Kanji whom
you've turned into God.

2102
02:01:12,171 --> 02:01:15,106
l don't know whether
you're great or fool.

2103
02:01:15,507 --> 02:01:19,170
l kept telling you don't
turn religion into business..

2104
02:01:19,211 --> 02:01:23,170
..you made him God and
started your business.

2105
02:01:24,650 --> 02:01:26,174
Tell me one thing.

2106
02:01:26,485 --> 02:01:30,683
The world's so beautiful,
why should God live only in temples?

2107
02:01:31,690 --> 02:01:33,920
l say, have faith in Him.

2108
02:01:34,493 --> 02:01:35,585
Believe in Him from your heart..

2109
02:01:35,661 --> 02:01:36,889
..and you will find God.

2110
02:01:37,696 --> 02:01:40,221
Try to find God in humans,
and you will find Him.

2111
02:01:40,532 --> 02:01:42,523
You will find Him in humans.

2112
02:01:42,601 --> 02:01:44,569
Not in these stones.

2113
02:01:45,737 --> 02:01:49,002
Not in these...stones.

2114
02:01:57,616 --> 02:01:59,880
They played with our emotions.

2115
02:01:59,985 --> 02:02:01,145
We won't spare them!

2116
02:02:01,186 --> 02:02:02,483
We won't spare them!

2117
02:02:02,521 --> 02:02:04,045
They spread the rumour
of your death as well.

2118
02:02:04,089 --> 02:02:05,750
They are the imposters.

2119
02:02:05,824 --> 02:02:07,485
Listen.

2120
02:02:07,926 --> 02:02:10,895
You kill two and there
are two hundred more.

2121
02:02:10,963 --> 02:02:12,658
Don't you see it on
television everyday?

2122
02:02:12,931 --> 02:02:15,627
Their real punishment is..

2123
02:02:15,767 --> 02:02:18,167
..let them leave respectfully.

2124
02:02:19,137 --> 02:02:22,129
Let them leave in
their expensive cars.

2125
02:02:22,207 --> 02:02:27,975
And no one will set foot
in their temples or hermitages.

2126
02:02:28,046 --> 02:02:29,513
Get that.

2127
02:02:29,581 --> 02:02:31,572
That will be their real punishment.

2128
02:02:32,517 --> 02:02:33,916
Please leave.

2129
02:03:01,113 --> 02:03:06,813
Faith and belief,
are very addictive, Kanji.

2130
02:03:08,086 --> 02:03:12,648
Once you're addicted to it,
you cannot let go easily.

2131
02:03:13,525 --> 02:03:15,516
All the people that you see here..

2132
02:03:16,528 --> 02:03:21,522
..they are not God-loving people,
they are God-fearing.

2133
02:03:22,067 --> 02:03:26,094
Sooner or later, you might
see them in hermitages again.

2134
02:03:29,875 --> 02:03:32,036
Be fearless!

2135
02:03:42,487 --> 02:03:45,979
So...won't you go along?

2136
02:03:47,559 --> 02:03:49,026
Come on, break the idol.

2137
02:03:50,462 --> 02:03:51,759
Papa.
- Where? Where is he?

2138
02:03:51,830 --> 02:03:57,496
l want you to promise that
no one will ever drop a penny..

2139
02:03:57,569 --> 02:03:59,537
..at any of the relegious places.

2140
02:04:04,443 --> 02:04:05,603
What are you staring at?

2141
02:04:05,677 --> 02:04:07,076
Break the statue.

2142
02:04:22,127 --> 02:04:25,563
Here, come here.
- Come, l'll introduce you to Krishna.

2143
02:04:25,630 --> 02:04:27,962
What?
- Come that way.

2144
02:04:33,071 --> 02:04:35,471
Look, Kanji bhai,
they're felling the statue.

2145
02:04:40,512 --> 02:04:42,639
lt's exactly like you wanted.

2146
02:04:43,582 --> 02:04:45,174
Look..

2147
02:05:04,503 --> 02:05:06,061
Who are you looking for, Kanji?

2148
02:05:08,974 --> 02:05:10,999
Didn't l say l am present everywhere?

2149
02:05:11,777 --> 02:05:14,041
l am pouring on fields as the rain.

2150
02:05:14,813 --> 02:05:17,145
And making nests along with the birds.

2151
02:05:17,949 --> 02:05:20,747
l am also taking lunch
with the ants down there.

2152
02:05:27,893 --> 02:05:29,690
Are you fine?
- Papa.

2153
02:05:30,095 --> 02:05:31,187
Yes, l am fine.

2154
02:05:31,496 --> 02:05:33,521
Whom did you want us to introduce to?

2155
02:05:37,002 --> 02:05:38,526
No one.

2156
02:05:38,804 --> 02:05:40,169
No one.

2157
02:05:42,574 --> 02:05:44,041
What are you doing, Kanji?

2158
02:05:44,810 --> 02:05:47,142
Don't wear this around
your neck as a talisman.

2159
02:05:48,113 --> 02:05:50,809
You finally succeeded
in explaining people..

2160
02:05:50,882 --> 02:05:52,474
..that this is wrong.

2161
02:05:52,717 --> 02:05:54,514
Throw it.

2162
02:05:54,753 --> 02:05:56,687
Throw it away.

